{
  "stem": "19921.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A pot with water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a special pot, you know, to wash yourself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he couldn't-- he couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he asked me for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He asked me for the toothbrush.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he washed himself, and about 10 minutes later, he was gone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he's still in my eyes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can't forget.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Same thing with my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father passed away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were myself there, Uncle David-- which is my mother's brother, the oldest brother-- and my mother, my grandfather, and the doctor in attendance.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it happened-- the doctor was there through whole night, and it happened 6 o'clock in the morning that night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was also with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That-- those memories don't go away, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They should, but they don't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother managed strictly whatever she had in saving, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then family helped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As you know, in Europe, there was no welfare or something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Families always stepped in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a large family on my mother's side, and they were doing pretty good for themselves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody just helped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, her parents were living with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her parents was living with us in that home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had also a uncle, what-- there was a building-- apartment to the house, and he had a-- his own apartment, but also in the same building.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was-- in other words, the families was close.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother's sister, she had three children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she had her own apartment, but it was just in the same-- in the-- we-- in other words, the same ground, attached home.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were living all there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother-- of course, my mother's parents were living with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had their own apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Just, you know, a room.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
